Hi
Add me
I am not on medication

Painful thing is I can't do things as I other people do normally. Like people do communication and job and etc things normally but  I don't do those and it is so hard for me I can't even imagine to do it.

My mood is like swings. Some days I got better but immediately I feel horrible. I lost my all interest in life. Things used to make me joy is not giving me joy anymore. All things are annoying me. Even talking to my parents and answering to their simple questions annoyed me. I just constantly wish how to live short as possible. I don't wanna live longer. If possible I wanna die right now even. I don't wanna go out and wanna be bed in all day. But I know its impossible. I need to go out and try to get a job. Anyway I don't think I suddenly became like this. I was like this as far as I know. I was that weird kid among others. And still I am. Feeling u comfortable around people. And feeling so uncomfortable living. And now I even became rude. I think its cuz of my constant dark thoughts or just this life is unbearable. I know they r people out there who is really in worst situations but it doesn't make me feel better even a bit. I feel so week. And I cry without any reason. Before I never cried. Now I got really changed emotionally. Tbh I don't wanna be like this and I try to change it but as much as I try as much as I hurt more. Became rude.

lately I became so rude and angry. I used to worry for people rather than my own feelings so I fake it to make them feel better. Then now I got selfish I prefer my feelings rather than them. I got angry at my parents and etc. It's getting serious. I got so different than before. I don't think I can live. I used to worry my family will suffer if I kill myself and now I don't even want to think others I just wanna do it anyway. Idk. Just telling myself one more day and I can die tommorow so I can live one more day. I never felt this bad before. 25 years old is too old for me. I can't believe I lived for 25 years. Its already so long enough. I wish I could donate my life to somebody in needs of it.
